   "source": [
    "#Making a simple function so that the results of the ADF Test become more readable\n",
    "\n",
    "def adfCheck(timeseries):\n",
    "    result=adfuller(timeseries) #This result will contain the 4 values given by the ADF Test\n",
    "    titles=['ADF Stats Test','p-value','Lag','No. of Obs']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for a,b in zip(result, titles):\n",
    "        print(b + \" : \" + str(a))\n",
    "        \n",
    "    if result[1]<=0.05:  #The index=1 of result contains the p-value\n",
    "        print(\"TimeSeries is Stationary bc Null Hypothesis is False/Rejected\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(\"TimeSeries is non-stationary bc Null Hypothesis is True/Accepted\")"
   ]
  },
